      <section endTime="1681.59" startTime="1533.71" type="report">
        <TEXT>
          <turn endTime="1595.853" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1533.71"><s>Guvernul<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">SUA</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e1" eiid="ei267" eventID="e1" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PAST">a anun&tcedil;at</EVENT>recent noi reglement&abreve;ri<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_STATE" eid="e3" eiid="ei268" eventID="e3" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PASTPART">proiectate</EVENT>pentru a<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e5" eiid="ei269" eventID="e5" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">schimba</EVENT>modul &icirc;n care organele pentru transplant sunt f&abreve;cute disponibile pacien&tcedil;ilor bolnavi .</s> <s>Sub noile dispozi&tcedil;ii , organele de_la donatori vor fi f&abreve;cute disponibile mai &icirc;nt&acirc;i celor mai bolnavi oameni , oriunde locuiesc &icirc;n &tcedil;ar&abreve; .</s> <s>&Icirc;n prezent , organele pentru transplant sunt ra&tcedil;ionalizate printr- un sistem regional de distribu&tcedil;ie .</s><s>Grupul privat care<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e11" eiid="ei270" eventID="e11" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">conduce</EVENT>sistemul current , Re&tcedil;eaua Unit&abreve; pentru Distribuirea Organelor , sau<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">UNOS</ENAMEX>, obiecteaz&abreve; la noile reglement&abreve;ri .</s> <s><ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">UNOS</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e13" eiid="ei271" eventID="e13" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">spune</EVENT>c&abreve; reglemet&abreve;rile<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e15" eiid="ei272" eventID="e15" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PAST">&icirc;ns&abreve;rcineaz&abreve;</EVENT>guvernul federal<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e16" eiid="ei273" eventID="e16" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESPART">s&abreve; decid&abreve;</EVENT>cine<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e17" eiid="ei274" eventID="e17" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">prime&scedil;te</EVENT><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e18" eiid="ei275" eventID="e18" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">transplante</EVENT>&scedil;i c&abreve; multe centre de transplant din spitale ar fi<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e19" eiid="ei276" eventID="e19" modality="would" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">for&tcedil;ate</EVENT>s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e22" eiid="ei277" eventID="e22" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">se &icirc;nchid&abreve;</EVENT>.</s><s><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Secretarul</ENAMEX>pentru S&abreve;n&abreve;tate &scedil;i<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Servicii<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Umane</ENAMEX>Donna Shalala</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e23" eiid="ei278" eventID="e23" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">spune</EVENT>c&abreve; pacien&tcedil;ii care au <EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_STATE" eid="e24" eiid="ei279" eventID="e24" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="PRESENT">nevoie</EVENT> de un<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e25" eiid="ei280" eventID="e25" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">transplant</EVENT>de organe nu ar trebui s&abreve;-&scedil;i <EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e30" eiid="ei282" eventID="e30" modality="should have to" polarity="NEG" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">&icirc;ncerce norocul</EVENT>ca un organ s&abreve; <EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e31" eiid="ei283" eventID="e31" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="FUTURE">devin&abreve;</EVENT>disponibil &icirc;n zona lor local&abreve; , &scedil;i nici n- ar trebui ca pacien&tcedil;ii s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e34" eiid="ei285" eventID="e34" modality="should have to" polarity="NEG" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">c&abreve;l&abreve;toreasc&abreve;</EVENT>la centre de transplant departe de casele lor pentru a- &scedil;i<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e38" eiid="ei286" eventID="e38" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">&icirc;mbun&abreve;t&abreve;&tcedil;i</EVENT>&scedil;ansele de a <EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e39" eiid="ei287" eventID="e39" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESPART">primi</EVENT>un organ .</s> <s><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Purt&abreve;toarea de cuv&acirc;nt</ENAMEX>a UNOS<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Donna Henry Wright</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e40" eiid="ei288" eventID="e40" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">spune</EVENT>c&abreve; noul regulament nu ar fi neap&abreve;rat mai<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e121" eiid="ei319" eventID="e121" modality="would" polarity="NEG" pos="ADJECTIVE" tense="NONE">drept</EVENT>sau<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e122" eiid="ei320" eventID="e122" modality="would" polarity="NEG" pos="ADJECTIVE" tense="NONE">eficient</EVENT>deoarece<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e43" eiid="ei290" eventID="e43" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">se fac</EVENT>deja concesii pentru pacien&tcedil;ii cei mai nevoia&scedil;i .</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1620.527" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1595.853"><s>Pacien&tcedil;ii cei mai bolnavi sunt deja<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e44" eiid="ei291" eventID="e44" polarity="POS" pos="ADJECTIVE" tense="PRESENT">trata&tcedil;i</EVENT>primii .</s> <s>Nu exist&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e45" eiid="ei292" eventID="e45" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="PRESENT">a&scedil;tept&abreve;ri</EVENT>mari &abreve;&abreve; - decal&abreve;ri enorme ale timpului de a&scedil;teptare printre pacien&tcedil;ii foarte &abreve;&abreve; cei mai bolnavi .</s><s>Este &icirc;ntre<CARDINAL>dou&abreve;_&scedil;i_&scedil;ase</CARDINAL>zile pentru fiecare &abreve;&abreve; dintre cei mai bolnavi pacien&tcedil;ii din &tcedil;ar&abreve; .</s> <s>Deci este o- este o &icirc;n&scedil;el&abreve;torie c&abreve;<EVENT aspect="PROGRESSIVE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e48" eiid="ei294" eventID="e48" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">fac</EVENT>asta pentru_c&abreve; cei mai bolnavi pacien&tcedil;i nu sunt<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e52" eiid="ei295" eventID="e52" polarity="NEG" pos="VERB" tense="PAST">servi&tcedil;i</EVENT>.</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1632.513" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1620.527">
            <s><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Doctorul James Burdick</ENAMEX>, profesorul de<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Chirurgia transplantului la Universitatea Johns Hopkins</ENAMEX>din<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Baltimore</ENAMEX>,<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Maryland</ENAMEX>, &scedil;i fost pre&scedil;edinte al<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">UNOS</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e53" eiid="ei296" eventID="e53" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PAST">a spus</EVENT>c&abreve; sistemul curent a<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e54" eiid="ei297" eventID="e54" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">evoluat</EVENT>pe parcursul<TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="false" tid="t103" type="DURATION" value="PXY">mai multor ani</TIMEX3>&scedil;i<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e55" eiid="ei298" eventID="e55" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">merge</EVENT>bine .</s>
          </turn>
          <turn endTime="1663.384" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1632.513"><s>S- ar putea , &icirc;ntr-<TIMEX3 anchorTimeID="t95" functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="true" tid="t105" type="DATE" value="FUTURE_REF">un an sau<CARDINAL>doi</CARDINAL></TIMEX3>,<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e56" eiid="ei299" eventID="e56" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">s&abreve; salv&abreve;m</EVENT>pu&tcedil;in mai multe vie&tcedil;i<SIGNAL sid="s57">dac&abreve;</SIGNAL><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e58" eiid="ei300" eventID="e58" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">ne ocup&abreve;m</EVENT>&icirc;nt&acirc;i de cei mai bolnavi .</s><s>Dar num&abreve;rul de pacien&tcedil;i care<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e59" eiid="ei301" eventID="e59" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESPART">a&scedil;teapt&abreve;</EVENT><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e60" eiid="ei302" eventID="e60" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">&icirc;ncepe</EVENT>atunci s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e62" eiid="ei303" eventID="e62" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">creasc&abreve;</EVENT>, &scedil;i , de_fapt , peste<TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="false" tid="t106" type="DURATION" value="PXY">ani</TIMEX3>s-ar<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e67" eiid="ei305" eventID="e67" modality="would" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">acumula</EVENT>mult mai mul&tcedil;i pacien&tcedil;i care sunt gata s&abreve; moar&abreve; f&abreve;r&abreve; un<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e65" eiid="ei304" eventID="e65" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">transplant</EVENT>de ficat .</s><s>Dac&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e68" eiid="ei306" eventID="e68" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">mergi</EVENT>pe extrema alternativ&abreve; , nu<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e69" eiid="ei307" eventID="e69" polarity="NEG" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">salvezi</EVENT>la_fel_de multe vie&tcedil;i &icirc;n<TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="false" tid="t118" type="DURATION" value="PXY">primii ani</TIMEX3>,</s> <s>Sistemul nostru<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e119" eiid="ei308" eventID="e119" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">este</EVENT>balansat , este chiar la mijloc .</s> <s>&Scedil;i , prin_urmare ,<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e120" eiid="ei309" eventID="e120" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">merge</EVENT>foarte bine .</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1681.59" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1663.384">
            <s>&Icirc;n toat&abreve; na&tcedil;iunea sunt<CARDINAL>cam zece_mii</CARDINAL>de pacien&tcedil;i care<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e72" eiid="ei310" eventID="e72" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESPART">a&scedil;teapt&abreve;</EVENT><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e73" eiid="ei311" eventID="e73" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">transplante</EVENT>de ficat<TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" quant="EACH" temporalFunction="false" tid="t107" type="SET" value="P1Y">&icirc;n fiecare an</TIMEX3>&scedil;i numai<CARDINAL>patru_mii</CARDINAL>de organe<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e74" eiid="ei312" eventID="e74" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">devin</EVENT>disponibile pentru<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e75" eiid="ei313" eventID="e75" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">transplante</EVENT>.</s>
            <s><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Secretarul Shalala</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e76" eiid="ei314" eventID="e76" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">spune</EVENT><ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">UNOS</ENAMEX><TIMEX3 anchorTimeID="t95" functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="true" tid="t108" type="DATE" value="1997-10">de acum cinci luni</TIMEX3>, sau le-<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e77" eiid="ei315" eventID="e77" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PAST">a dat</EVENT><TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="false" tid="t109" type="DURATION" value="P5M"><CARDINAL>cinci</CARDINAL>luni</TIMEX3>s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e79" eiid="ei316" eventID="e79" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">-&scedil;i dezvolte</EVENT>un<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_STATE" eid="e111" eiid="ei317" eventID="e111" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">plan</EVENT>nou de a<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e81" eiid="ei318" eventID="e81" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">distribui</EVENT>fica&tcedil;ii care sunt &icirc;n rezerva cea mai apropiat&abreve; .</s>
            <s>Aici<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">VOA</ENAMEX>Ast&abreve;zi .</s>
          </turn>
